@startuml elecGroupId-双路径传导-简化版
' ============================================================
' elecGroupId V2 双路径汇合传导 — 简化时序图
' 目标：介绍双路径如何传导 elecGroupId 到 RankDesc
'       以及子通信域如何继承、ocsPlaneId/Num 如何生成
' ============================================================

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 40

title elecGroupId 双路径传导 — 简化时序图

actor "Client" as Client

box "Path A - RootInfo 自协商" #E8F5E9
    participant "ConstructRankTable\nrank_info_detect_client.cc" as PathA_Parse
    participant "BinaryStream\n序列化" as PathA_Ser
    participant "TCP Server\n合并 & 广播" as PathA_Server
end box

box "Path B - ClusterInfo RankTable" #E3F2FD
    participant "HcclCommInitClusterInfoV2\nop_base_v2.cc" as PathB_Api
    participant "InitRankGraph string\ncommunicator_impl.cc:1290" as PathB_Init
end box

box "汇合点" #FFF3E0
    participant "InitRankGraph\nRankTableInfo&\ncommunicator_impl.cc:1329" as Merge
end box

box "RankGraph 构建 & 写入" #F3E5F5
    participant "RankGraphBuilder\nBuildRankGraph" as Builder
    participant "RankGraph\nBuildRankDescVec" as RankGraph
    participant "ReparseGroupedPlane\nForOcsMesh" as Reparse
    database "rankDescVec_\nvector<RankDesc>" as Vec
end box

box "子通信域" #FFEBEE
    participant "CreateSubComm\ncommunicator_impl.cc:324" as SubComm
end box

== Path A - RootInfo Self-Negotiation ==

Client -> PathA_Parse: Read /etc/hccl_rootinfo.json
PathA_Parse -> PathA_Parse: RankLevelInfo::Deserialize\n  elecGroupId = json.value<u32>("elec_group_id", 0)
note over PathA_Parse: elecGroupId: JSON → C++ u32

PathA_Parse -> PathA_Ser: GetBinStream << elecGroupId
PathA_Ser -> PathA_Server: TCP Send Client→Server

PathA_Server -> PathA_Server: BinaryStream >> elecGroupId\nMerge all clients, no modify
PathA_Server -> PathA_Ser: Broadcast BinaryStream << elecGroupId
PathA_Ser -> PathA_Parse: BinaryStream >> elecGroupId\nrootInfoUpdate repeat serialize round

PathA_Parse -> Merge: Init(RankTableInfo)\n  → InitRankGraph(RankTableInfo&)
note over Merge: RankTableInfo.ranks[i]\n  .rankLevelInfos[j].elecGroupId

== Path B - ClusterInfo RankTable File ==

Client -> PathB_Api: HcclCommInitClusterInfoV2
PathB_Api -> PathB_Api: HcomLoadRankTableFileV2\nread JSON file to std::string
note over PathB_Api: ranktableM 含 "elec_group_id": N\n原始 JSON 文本, 未解析

PathB_Api -> PathB_Init: Init(string ranktableM)

PathB_Init -> PathB_Init: JsonParser::ParseString\n  → RankLevelInfo::Deserialize\n    elecGroupId = json.value<u32>("elec_group_id", 0)
note over PathB_Init: 唯一一次 JSON → C++

PathB_Init -> Merge: InitRankGraph(RankTableInfo&)

== Convergence - BuildRankDescVec ==

Merge -> Builder: RankGraphBuilder::Build ranktable, topoPath, myRank
Builder -> Builder: BuildRankGraph phase 1-7\n  BuildFromRankTable, BuildPeer2PeerLinks...

Builder -> RankGraph: BuildRankDescVec *rankTable_ phase 8

group BuildRankDescVec detail
    RankGraph -> Vec: assign count, RankDesc{}
    loop i = 0 .. count-1
        RankGraph -> RankGraph: globalIdx = globalRankIds ? rankIds[i] : i
        RankGraph -> RankGraph: rankInfo = rankTable.ranks[globalIdx]
        RankGraph -> RankGraph: for each rankLevelInfo:\n  if OCS_MESH: d.elecGroupId = lv.elecGroupId
    end
    RankGraph -> Reparse: ReparseGroupedPlaneForOcsMesh rankTable, globalRankIds
end

== ocsPlaneId ocsPlaneNum Generation ==

Reparse -> Reparse: for each OCS_MESH netInst, group rankIds\n  by elecGroupId read from RankTableInfo
Reparse -> Reparse: totalGroups = elecGroups size\nplaneIdx = 0,1,2...
Reparse -> Vec: for each group, for each rankId:\n  rankDescVec_[rankId].ocsPlaneId = planeIdx\n  rankDescVec_[rankId].ocsPlaneNum = totalGroups

Merge -> Merge: save ranktableInfo from builder for sub-comm use

== Sub-communicator Inheritance ==

Client -> SubComm: CreateSubComm rankIds
SubComm -> RankGraph: CreateSubRankGraph rankIds
SubComm -> RankGraph: BuildRankDescVec *ranktableInfo &rankIds
note over RankGraph: d.elecGroupId = lv.elecGroupId 子域与父域同源

SubComm -> SubComm: subCommImpl->Init subRankGraph
note over SubComm: 子域 Init 不重建 RankGraph\nranktableInfo 保持 nullptr\nBuildRankDescVec 在 Init 之前已完成

@enduml
